    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/5b1ee3d1ef571012db4c98c175fd9112.avif?t=1767361264\" width=760 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/e2fd8a7873b0d7c3939c0998c80ae3d5.webp?t=1767361264\" width=253 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mops &amp; Mobs <strong>demo</strong> showcases the <strong>entire first level</strong> and introduces all key mechanics of the full game, from narrative dialogue and card-based combat to room decoration, puzzle-solving, and detective-style investigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/3f260aa5dd34155d8adb475608eba516.avif?t=1767361264\" width=760 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/30c73c3819689a63a74a704e6562d838.webp?t=1767361264\" width=391 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…there was a <strong>hero</strong> entering a dungeon, like so many did before them. But this one - <strong>you!</strong> - is not up for murder. They're looking for a <strong>job</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mops &amp; Mobs</strong> is set in the bowels of a <strong>multi-level labyrinth</strong> where you’re going to meet monsters in <strong>critical moments</strong> of their lives - as the dungeon recently was inherited by a new owner who doesn’t quite know what he’s doing. But it’s not just the dungeon’s <strong>master who is struggling ...</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Befriend a cast of charmingly unhinged monsters</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/3ed0e4e460da38df97f30114e7d4544d.poster.avif?t=1767361264\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/3ed0e4e460da38df97f30114e7d4544d.webm?t=1767361264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>lich lady</strong> lamenting her past, a<strong> gelatinous cube</strong> befallen by an existential crisis, the <strong>prison guard</strong> longing for immortality - even the <strong>bridge troll</strong> is being kept from his purpose… <strong>Talk </strong>to the monsters, <strong>get to know them</strong>, <strong>find out</strong> what troubles them and <strong>help </strong>where you can.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Explore a retro-styled dungeon in a juicy dungeon crawler manner</strong> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/e6740d2ac35d744b35b4bd2e91001f4a.poster.avif?t=1767361264\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/e6740d2ac35d744b35b4bd2e91001f4a.webm?t=1767361264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dungeon is not your enemy -  <strong>it’s your workplace</strong>. <strong>Explore </strong>your new home from the greasy kitchen, the ancient library, the gold hoard the place where they do the bookkeeping, to the spooky graveyard, the hidden corridors, the fiery forge and all the other places where <strong>adventurers usually go to die</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Clean, repair, and redecorate rooms for monsters and vibes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/652c288d1ce6d194d7cfdad299bdd654.poster.avif?t=1767361264\" width=500 height=281 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/652c288d1ce6d194d7cfdad299bdd654.webm?t=1767361264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clear </strong>dirt heaps full of critters, <strong>learn</strong> each monster’s decoration style, and make the dungeon a better place for everyone. Even adventurers appreciate a <strong>well-maintained torture device</strong> from time to time!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Uncover the secret of a forgotten war like a detective </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/d6c1b15a79cb7451c337aa880325b408.poster.avif?t=1767361264\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/d6c1b15a79cb7451c337aa880325b408.webm?t=1767361264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dungeon master may deny it, but something is very wrong. <strong>A conspiracy</strong> is forming in the shadows and beyond. <strong>Investigate</strong> in <strong>detective manner</strong>: <strong>interrogate</strong>,<strong> find evidence</strong>, <strong>solve </strong>puzzles, <strong>combine </strong>clues and <strong>decipher </strong>hidden symbols.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Fight with collectible cards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/1ea6cf81c1460db950c4c4a57766ba05.poster.avif?t=1767361264\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/1ea6cf81c1460db950c4c4a57766ba05.webm?t=1767361264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Everyone plays cards</strong> in the dungeon. The monsters, adventurers, rats and even dirt heaps! Is it less bloody? Perhaps! <strong>Less deadly? Not. At. All!</strong> <strong>Help </strong>monsters in order to <strong>gain special cards</strong> and build a deck to have the upper hand.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Enjoy the twist on a beloved setting</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3064340/extras/0b9d81402b991150edec9cf1932399b9.avif?t=1767361264\" width=760 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mops &amp; Mobs delivers <strong>office humour meets role-playing narratives </strong>- while taking its cast <strong>very serious</strong>. Take a look behind the scenes of a dungeon business, where monsters are your <strong>co-workers</strong> and adventurers your <strong>customers</strong>.</p>",
